{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aff4fe01e8","title":"人民大学宗派主义根源在党中央","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4c63fc6afa","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"aff4fe01e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"09850b8d0e","name":"汪同祖"},{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ed7cec3170","type":"title","text":"人民大学宗派主义根源在党中央","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"7650fe959b","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学汪同祖","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"17684c6914","type":"subtitle","text":"（汪同祖：中国人民大学新闻系外语教研室副教授）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"35e34b7dd3","type":"paragraph","text":"人民大学一开办就竖起了两面大旗；一面是教条主义，一面是宗派主义。教条主义的根源是由于学习苏联。宗派主义是由于党团员多，根源在党中央。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"a128e16084","type":"paragraph","text":"学校象衙门，而学术空气不浓，过份强调政治，学术次要的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"dec495bd5a","type":"paragraph","text":"人民大学是个党员很多非党同志很少的一个大学，所以党群这座墙就很难推倒。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"f9dfb4a185","type":"paragraph","text":"首先应该去掉几个副校长。我们要那么多副校长干什么？！他们不懂业务，不知道干些什么！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"4515f83137","type":"paragraph","text":"人大的行政干部对待知识分子是秀才碰着兵，有理说不清。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"},{"id":"615ab5c3ca","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8"}],"page":{"id":"f93b3c5dc7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aff4fe01e8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}